# Frontend-Specific Guidelines

## Next.js Specific Guidelines
- Use Pages Router (not App Router) for this project
- Implement proper SEO with meta tags and structured data
- Use Next.js Image component for optimized images
- Use getServerSideProps for dynamic content that needs SEO

## React Component Patterns
- Use functional components with hooks exclusively
- Follow component composition patterns over inheritance
- Use React.memo for expensive components when appropriate
- Implement proper error boundaries for component trees

## Frontend-Specific State Management
- Use Zustand for client-side state management
- Keep state as close to components as possible
- Use React hooks for local component state
- Implement proper loading and error states

## Frontend Performance
- Use lazy loading for heavy components
- Implement code splitting for large components
- Optimize bundle size with tree shaking
- Use proper image optimization strategies